@startuml
!theme plain

title Diagramme de sequence - Gestion equipements

autonumber

actor Administrateur
boundary Frontend as "Application Angular"
control API as "Backend Spring Boot"
control ServiceEq as "Service Equipement"
database DB as "Base de donnees"

Administrateur -> Frontend: Declarer maintenance equipement
Frontend -> API: PUT /equipements/{id}/maintenance
API -> ServiceEq: verifierEtatCourant(id)
ServiceEq -> DB: Lire equipement
DB --> ServiceEq: Etat equipement

alt Equipement disponible
  ServiceEq -> DB: Mettre a jour etat=MAINTENANCE
  DB --> ServiceEq: Mise a jour OK
  ServiceEq --> API: Statut modifie
  API --> Frontend: 200 OK
  Frontend --> Administrateur: Afficher succes
else Equipement introuvable ou deja hors service
  ServiceEq --> API: Erreur metier
  API --> Frontend: 409 Conflict
  Frontend --> Administrateur: Afficher alerte
end

@enduml
